{"tid":250782,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊老師(小學) 可唔可以入一入黎","createTime":"2017-05-20T10:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T06:43:57.000Z","uid":71654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"795b812ee473359ae945b1c47e32f8974ed3e37a","tid":250782,"uid":71654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"上年畢業 搵到份小學合約<br />\n前日見校長 傾續約嘅問題<br />\n竟然開個perm位比我<br />\n但係其實呢間都真係好chur<br />\n我交英文常識電腦 再加班主任 課外活動<br />\n七點幾返到七點幾八點先走<br />\n<br />\n但係其實如果我唔要個常額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家會唔會好難搵工<br />\n我怕我合約都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋各位覺得<br />\n如果我去面試嘅時候<br />\n我話我其實依家有常額 人哋會唔會用啲俾perm我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求解答"},{"pid":"dd88af0bfbc89be7521b4c27e2f9202795a66fb7","tid":250782,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"做住先，再轉"},{"pid":"7e8471c47a6b8f74d54ebcd4ca970b3f34032274","tid":250782,"uid":23293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:27:31.000Z","msg":"緊係做咗先, 一日未轉到, 你都唔係常額..."},{"pid":"872b50c64872872544901e3fb4db810c0966e0cd","tid":250782,"uid":71654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T12:13:29.000Z","msg":"我都知我應該簽左先<br />\n我依家都搵緊工<br />\n我係諗緊如果比到份合約我<br />\n我究竟繼續喺度好常額好<br />\n定係有合約就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e256528ccf964d2956c7e291f96d33ba4123e038","tid":250782,"uid":65551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:43:57.000Z","msg":"做住先啦<br />\n忙都有忙嘅好 試多啲嘢，轉去做第份見工時CV都靚啲啦<br />\n<br />\n我依家呢間都係好忙，大部分老師都係起碼六點先有人走"}]}